OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA few
OL,6,Fshowers, wintry on the hills, continue
OL,7,Fthrough the evening before clearing
OL,8,Ffrom the east by midnight. This will
OL,9,Fleave the rest of the night dry and
OL,10,Fcold with clear periods.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FDry and bright but frosty
OL,13,Fmorning, becoming cloudy from around
OL,14,Fmidday with outbreaks of rain and hill
OL,15,Fsnow in the afternoon. The wind will
OL,16,Fstrengthen towards the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
