OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FHeavy
OL,6,Frain, hill snow and gales or severe
OL,7,Fgales clear Sunday morning, leaving a
OL,8,Ffew afternoon showers. Mostly dry but
OL,9,Fcloudy Monday and Tuesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
